text: Špela Kolbl (born 13 March 1998) is a Slovenian footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Slovenia women's national team. ==Career== Kolbl has been capped for the Slovenia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian women's footballers Category:Slovenia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:ŽNK Pomurje players
